	and string.

	* pynits.py: Better handle multi-line list comprehensions.

2004-06-21  François Pinard  <pinard@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* pynits.py: Redesign refilling.  It was too aggressive, and could
	also be fooled by some triple-quoted strings.

	* pynits.py: Avoid raw for a string if the delimiter appears in it.

